<section id="command.groups.focres"><title>Forces Commands</title>
	
	<para>Calculate forces for models and trajectory frames.</para>

	<section id="command.ref.frameforces"><title>frameforces</title>
		<indexterm><primary>commands</primary><secondary>frameforces</secondary></indexterm>
		
		<para><emphasis>Syntax:</emphasis></para>
		<funcsynopsis>
			<funcprototype>
				<funcdef>void <function>frameforces</function></funcdef>
				<void/>
			</funcprototype>
		</funcsynopsis>
		<para>Calculate the atomic forces of the current frame of the trajectory associated with the current model.</para>
		
		<para>For example:</para>
		<synopsis>
			frameforces();
		</synopsis>
		
	</section>
	
